#: includes/eme-events.php:7478
msgid "By default the dynamic data check only happens for the fields mentioned in your dynamic data condition if those are present in your RSVP form definition. Using this option, you can use all booking placeholders, even if not defined in your RSVP form. The small disadvantage is that more requests will be made to the backend, so use only when absolutely needed."
